data.name: CannotLoadCustomDataTypeError
data.value: Custom data type '{0}' cannot be loaded. Please make sure it is defined and can be referenced in the application.

data.name: Instructions
data.value:
Use this page to edit an existing profile property.
You can make properties part of a group (such as a billing address group).
You can change data type of each property, either a native .NET type or a custom type (class).
For custom types, provide the namespace and class name.

data.name: PropertyNameHasBeenDefinedError
data.value: Property name has already been defined as an existing property or group
